sterone to androstenedione, respectively (Burris-Hiday &amp; Scott, 2021; Miller &amp; Auchus, 2011, 2019; Peng et al., 2019; Wr&oacute;bel et al., 2023). If either of these reactions are inhibited, it can lead to decreased androstenedione levels.", "timestamp": "Mon Jun 08 15:16:44 +0000 2026"}